_sText:
I made this map, because when i watched AvP (the film) i realy liked the labyrinth idea. So i decaded to make something similar. In this map are the floors, walls and the ceiling changeing in 10-20 seconds. There are traps too, so be careful! :) 
Specail thanks to UMBRELLAJackson for his/her helicopter.: http://www.gamebanana.com/css/prefabs/2331

Extract to counter-strike source folder. Works with bots but much more fun to play with friends/enemies :)

Thanks for download and have fun!
